    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_2255163573" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2255163573" />
    <a title="Kristy K" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/32383826-kristy-k"><img alt="Kristy K" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1471737220p2/32383826.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2255163573?book_show_action=true">Jan 27, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kristy K" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kristy K" href="/user/show/32383826-kristy-k">Kristy K</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32383826-kristy-k?shelf=sociology">sociology</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32383826-kristy-k?shelf=2020">2020</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/32383826-kristy-k?shelf=true-crime">true-crime</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2255163573" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2628205007057792446">3.5 Stars<br/><br/>A look into murder and policing in LA’s roughest areas. It’s written by a journalist who spent years sharing an office with some LAPD homicide detectives. She focuses on one particular murder case using it as a jumping point to discuss the other issues at large such as gangs, black on black violence, inadequate policing, and overworked homicide detectives. A great book focusing on the sociological aspects of crime. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


