<li class='cover' id='bookCover_29502356'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29502356-locked-in"><img alt="Locked In: The True Causes of Mass Incarceration and How to Achieve Real Reform" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1458496191l/29502356._SX98_.jpg" />
